description: This hall of fame Yulenka purrs with a rating of 81, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 648, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Box for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [648 Votes, Hall of Fame]
